*To divide whole data to each day
*Avoiding segment fault
*By: suntian
*Data: 2011.04.17

$keys file day
 evaluate to runtime $day - 1
do n from 0 to %runtime 
 evaluate to t_begin $n * 86400
 evaluate to t_end $n * 86400 + 86400
 cut %t_begin %t_end
 r $file
* if $n lt 10
*  w 0$n$day.SAC
* else
  w $n$day.SAC
* endif
 cut off
enddo
